						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">smear </div><br /><br />If you swapped sprites every frame...and half of the frames had transparent bits where the other had solid bits...it would look blurry (on a CRT). On a flatscreen TV, it will probably not work correctly at all. (IDK)<br /><br />Shifting sprites in VRAM byte by byte is not trivial. This effect should be pre-rendered.<br /><br />(Edited)</div>

					
