			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I would definitely pre-render the ship at different angles. That's how Solar Jetman does it (it's a spaceship but the concept is the exact same), and it's a great NES game. Also with flipping you can reuse many angles, so you only have to pre-render angles between 0° and 90° and the rest is obtained by flipping existing frames. So with something like 5 or 6 angles you're done, there's really no need to do anything more complex.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

